{
    "info": {
        "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890",
        "name": "Selcom Payments API - Sokolink",
        "description": "Complete API documentation for Selcom payment integration in the Sokolink marketplace platform. This collection includes endpoints for payment checkout, callback handling, and payment management.\n\n## Authentication\nMost endpoints require Bearer token authentication using Laravel Sanctum.\n\n## Base URL\n`{{base_url}}/api/v1`\n\n## Payment Flow\n1. User adds items to cart\n2. User initiates checkout with `/checkout` endpoint\n3. System creates payment with Selcom and sends USSD push to user's phone\n4. User approves payment on their mobile device\n5. Selcom sends payment confirmation to `/payments/callback/selcom` webhook\n6. Order is created and payment status is updated\n\n## Payment Methods Supported\n- Mobile Money (via Selcom)\n  - M-Pesa (Vodacom Tanzania)\n  - Tigo Pesa\n  - Airtel Money\n  - Halopesa\n\n## Environment Variables Required\n- `base_url`: Your API base URL (e.g., https://api.sokolink.co.tz)\n- `bearer_token`: Authentication token from login\n- `payment_reference`: Reference ID for payment queries",
        "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
        "_exporter_id": "12345678"
    },
    "item": [
        {
            "name": "Checkout & Payment",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "Checkout Cart (Initiate Payment)",
                    "event": [
                        {
                            "listen": "test",
                            "script": {
                                "exec": [
                                    "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                                    "    const response = pm.response.json();",
                                    "    if (response.data && response.data.reference) {",
                                    "        pm.environment.set('payment_reference', response.data.reference);",
                                    "        console.log('Payment reference saved:', response.data.reference);",
                                    "    }",
                                    "}"
                                ],
                                "type": "text/javascript"
                            }
                        }
                    ],
                    "request": {
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Accept",
                                "value": "application/json",
                                "type": "text"
                            },
                            {
