                                "type": "text"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n    \"fullname\": \"John Doe\",\n    \"phone\": \"+255712345678\",\n    \"address_phone\": \"+255712345678\",\n    \"address\": \"123 Main Street, Kinondoni\",\n    \"region_id\": 1,\n    \"payment_method_id\": 1,\n    \"payment_option_id\": 1\n}",
                            "options": {
                                "raw": {
                                    "language": "json"
                                }
                            }
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/checkout",
                            "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                            "path": ["api", "v1", "checkout"]
                        },
                        "description": "Initiates the checkout process for items in the user's cart. Creates an order and initiates payment via Selcom mobile money.\n\n### Request Body Parameters\n\n| Field | Type | Required | Description | Example |\n|-------|------|----------|-------------|----------|\n| fullname | string | Yes | Full name of the buyer | \"John Doe\" |\n| phone | string | Yes | Mobile phone number (must be +255XXXXXXXXX format) | \"+255712345678\" |\n| address_phone | string | No | Alternative phone for delivery | \"+255712345678\" |\n| address | string | Yes | Full delivery address | \"123 Main Street, Kinondoni\" |\n| region_id | integer | Yes | Region ID for delivery | 1 |\n| payment_method_id | integer | Yes | Payment method ID (e.g., 1 for Mobile Money) | 1 |\n| payment_option_id | integer | Yes | Payment option ID (1=pay-now, 2=save-pay-later, 3=request-payment) | 1 |\n\n### Payment Options\n- **1** - Pay Now: Immediate payment initiation\n- **2** - Save & Pay Later: Creates order but defers payment\n- **3** - Request Payment: Sends payment request to customer\n\n### Response\nReturns payment initiation details including:\n- Payment reference ID\n- USSD prompt message\n- Payment status (pending)\n\n### Notes\n- User must have items in their cart\n- Phone number must be Tanzanian (+255 prefix)\n- For Selcom payments, user will receive USSD push notification on their phone\n- User must approve payment within the timeout period (usually 5 minutes)"
                    },
