                        "description": "Retrieves a paginated list of all payments for the authenticated user.\n\n### Query Parameters\n\n| Parameter | Type | Required | Description | Example |\n|-----------|------|----------|-------------|---------|\n| payment_method_id | integer | No | Filter payments by payment method | 1 |\n| status | string | No | Filter by payment status | pending, successful, failed, cancelled |\n| search | string | No | Search by order reference or payment reference | ORD-20250916-ABC123 |\n\n### Payment Statuses\n- **pending**: Payment initiated but not yet completed\n- **successful**: Payment completed successfully\n- **failed**: Payment failed or rejected\n- **cancelled**: Payment cancelled by user or system\n\n### Response\nReturns paginated list of payments with:\n- Payment ID and reference\n- Amount and status\n- Payment method details\n- Associated order information\n- Transaction timestamps"
                    },
