                        "description": "Retrieves detailed information about a specific payment by its ID.\n\n### Path Parameters\n\n| Parameter | Type | Required | Description | Example |\n|-----------|------|----------|-------------|---------|\n| id | integer | Yes | Payment ID | 101 |\n\n### Response\nReturns complete payment details including:\n- Payment reference and transaction ID\n- Amount and status\n- Payment method information\n- Order details\n- Callback data (for Selcom payments)\n- Timestamps\n\n### Error Responses\n- **404**: Payment not found\n- **401**: Unauthorized (missing or invalid token)"
