                        "description": "This endpoint receives payment status updates from the Selcom payment gateway. It is called automatically by Selcom when a payment is completed, failed, or cancelled.\n\n### Request Body (from Selcom)\n\n| Field | Type | Required | Description | Example |\n|-------|------|----------|-------------|---------|\n| result | string | Yes | Overall transaction result | SUCCESS, FAILED |\n| resultcode | string | Yes | Selcom result code | 000 (success), others for errors |\n| order_id | string | Yes | Selcom order ID | 602021152 |\n| transid | string | Yes | Selcom transaction ID | 7945454515 |\n| reference | string | Yes | Payment reference from your system | 856266164161 |\n| channel | string | No | Mobile money operator used | TIGOPESATZ, MPESATZ, AIRTELTZ, HALOPESATZ |\n| amount | string | Yes | Transaction amount in TZS | 50000 |\n| phone | string | Yes | Customer phone number | 255712345678 |\n| payment_status | string | Yes | Payment status | COMPLETED, FAILED, PENDING, CANCELLED |\n\n### Selcom Channels\n- **MPESATZ**: M-Pesa (Vodacom)\n- **TIGOPESATZ**: Tigo Pesa\n- **AIRTELTZ**: Airtel Money\n- **HALOPESATZ**: Halopesa\n\n### Payment Status Mapping\n- **SUCCESS + COMPLETED** → successful\n- **FAILED** → failed\n- **PENDING/PROCESSING** → pending\n- **CANCELLED** → cancelled\n\n### Workflow\n1. Selcom sends callback after payment attempt\n2. System validates callback data\n3. Payment record is updated with transaction ID and status\n4. If payment is successful and linked to cart:\n   - Order is created from cart items\n   - Cart is cleared\n   - Buyer receives confirmation SMS\n   - Sellers are notified\n5. Response is sent back to Selcom\n\n### Notes\n- This endpoint does NOT require authentication (it's called by Selcom)\n- All callbacks are logged for debugging\n- Callback data is stored in payment record\n- Duplicate callbacks are handled gracefully"
                    },
